Insider Activity


Individual




Thomas O. Ryder



Mr. Thomas O. Ryder is Independent Director at Quad/Graphics, Inc., Lead Independent Director at RPX Corp., Lead Independent Director at Amazon.com, Inc., and Independent Director at Starwood Hotels & Resorts Worldwide, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Quad/Graphics, Inc., RPX Corp., Amazon.com, Inc., Starwood Hotels & Resorts Worldwide, Inc., Sheraton Hotels & Resorts, and Sheraton Madison Hotel.
Mr. Ryder was previously employed as Lead Independent Director by World Color Press, Inc., Chairman by Virgin Mobile USA, Inc., Chairman by The Reader's Digest Association, Inc., President by American Express Travel Related Services Co., Inc., Chairman by Magazine Publishers of America, and President by Time, Inc. Affluent Media Group. He also served on the board at The Association of American Publishers and Direct Marketing Association, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Louisiana State University.



